Documentation is critical for Runa:

Update language reference for ANY syntax changes
Provide examples for every new feature
Document semantic intent, not just syntax
Keep tutorials up-to-date with changes
Generate training data from documentation

Documentation locations:

Language spec: runa/docs/language_reference/
Examples: runa/tests/examples/

Tutorials: runa/docs/tutorials/